data.text:
List of film actors and actresses from Taiwan, listed alphabetically with photos when available. Taiwan has produced some very talented actors and actresses in the last century, many of who have gone on to star in comedies, dramas, horror movies and more. These Taiwanese actors specialize in film, television or even theater, so they're not all necessarily movie stars. These are some of the best Taiwanese actors the country has ever seen, so if you're a native of Taiwan and an aspiring actor/actress then these are people you should look up to.

List actors range from Fang Fang to Shih Chin-hang.

This list answers the questions, "Who are the best Taiwanese actors?" and "Which movies stars are from Taiwan?"

You can click on the names of these legendary movie stars of Taiwan in order to get more information about each one. If you're a film buff use this list of talented Taiwanese film actors to find some new movies you haven't already seen.
